Title: White Hamburger Bun

Ingredients: FRENCH FRIES (POTATOES, VEGETABLE OIL SOYBEAN, CANOLA, COTTONSEED, AND/OR SUNFLOWER, CONTAINS LESS THAN 2 OF DEXTROSE, MALTODEXTRIN, SEA SALT, TO MAINTAIN NATURAL COLOR TETRASODIUM PYROPHOSPHATE, DISODIUM DIHYDROGEN PYROPHOSPHATE), CANOLA  FRYER SHORTENING (Ingredients High Oleic Canola Oil with TBHQ and Citric Acid added to protect flavor, and Dimethylpolysiloxane added to reduce foaming.), SALT SHAKERS (SALT, SODIUM SILICOALUMINATE - THIS SALT DOES NOT SUPPLY IODIDE, A NECESSARY NUTRIENT.)
